==Starting off==
* {{tbox|Irena seems to be very upset and cries as your approach her.}}
* '''Irena:''' Boo hoo! Oh dear, my only daughter....
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|What's the matter?}}
** '''Player:''' What's the matter?
** '''Irena:''' Oh dear... my daughter, Ana, has gone missing in the desert. I fear that she is lost, or perhaps... *sob* even worse.
** '''Player:''' When did she go into the desert?
** '''Irena:''' *Sob* she went in there just a few days ago, *Sob* she said she would be back yesterday.
** '''Irena:''' *Sob* And she's not...
** {{tselect|Start The Tourist Trap quest?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'll find her for you!
*** '''Irena:''' Oh thank you! You've made me a very happy mother, I just hope it's not too late!
*** '''Player:''' Do you have any ideas on where she may have gone?
*** '''Irena:''' I did go looking for her myself and I came across some footprints just a little way south. I'm worried that they lead to the desert mining camp!
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** '''Player:''' Oh... Well I hope you find her.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Cheer up, it might never happen.}}
** '''Player:''' Cheer up, it might never happen.
** '''Irena:''' It may already have happened you thoughtless oaf! My daughter, Ana, has gone missing in the desert. I fear that she is lost, or perhaps... *sobs* even worse.
** '''Player:''' When did she go into the desert?
** '''Irena:''' *Sob* she went in there just a few days ago, *Sob* she said she would be back yesterday.
** {{tact|above}}

===Talking to Irena again===
* '''Irena:''' Please bring my daughter back to me. She is most likely list in the Desert somewhere. I miss her so much... Wahhhhh! *Sob*
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Do you know where Ana went?}}
** '''Player:''' Do you know where Ana went?
** '''Irena:''' I did look for her myself and a little way south. I came across some footprints which may be hers. I'm worried that she may have been caught by some guards and taken to work in that terrible desert mine to the south.
** {{tact|previous}}
* {{topt|Is there anywhere around here that she would go?}}
** '''Player:''' Is there anywhere around here that she would go?
** '''Irena:''' I think she may have just gone a little way into the desert. It's unlike her to go too far away. She is an adventurous girl, but she knows how I worry. She wouldn't go too far.
** {{tact|previous}}
* {{topt|Where do you think I should start my search?}}
** '''Player:''' Where do you think I should start my search?
** '''Irena:''' I think I saw some of her footprints to the south, you could start there. Hopefully she'll just be over a few sand dunes, but you never know. She may have been taken to that awful desert mining camp or captured by
** '''Irena:''' brigands!
** {{tact|previous}}
* {{topt|Okay, thanks.}}
** '''Player:''' Okay, thanks.
** {{tact|end}}

===Looking at the footprints===
* {{tbox|This looks like some disturbed sand. Footsteps seem to be heading off towards the South.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Searching the footprints===
* {{tbox|You search the footsteps more closely. You can see that there are five sets of footprints. One set of footprints seems lighter than the others. The four other footsteps were made by heavier people with boots.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Inspecting a cactus with a scarf on it===
* {{tbox|You remember that Irena mentioned something about Ana wearing a red scarf before she left for the desert.}}
* {{tact|end}}

