===Attempting to enter the gate without the key===
* {{mes|This gate needs a key in order to be opened.}}

===Searching the gate===
* {{tbox|You see what looks like a mining compound. There seems to be people mining rocks. They look as if they're chained to the rocks and they're being watched over by the guards. It's not a very happy place.}}
* {{tbox|You notice that people are thoroughly searched as they enter and leave the compound and people wielding weapons or wearing armour are treated quite severly.}}
* {{tact|end}}

